    this is tamplate engine in laravel ,that is plan text convert into php 
    why that do: beacuse that is php tag some time deficate to in code 
            
            @csrf 
            e.g:<?php ?> in php
                {{}}---- in laravel

                <?php echo $i;>
                {{$i}}---karavel
                ----------------------
                @if($user=='admin')
                <h1>hi {{$user}}
                @elseif($user="user")
                    <h>thso admin
                @end
                ---------------------
                @for($i=0;$i<10;$i++)
                @end
                ---------------
                @foreach($suer as $row)
                #endforeach

                =====================
                **include another file in blade.php**

                @include('inner')

                **Js in php**
                <script>
                    var data=@json($users);
                    console.log(data);
                </script>

